  A89.2 did-you-mean within edit-dist 2   →  symbol-table lookup · Levenshtein · single-best
                                              suggestion only · type-aware kind filter
  A89.3 ANSI color when stderr is tty     →  color::Style enum · IsTerminal check · NO_COLOR

